  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/b3e1e05afeea20b71a0ba55cc1dce031.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/b3e1e05afeea20b71a0ba55cc1dce031.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/b3e1e05afeea20b71a0ba55cc1dce031.mp4?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Psychroma is a psychological horror side-scroller set in a haunted cyberpunk house. Collect cards and explore the memories stored on them to piece together your past. But the deeper you go, the more you expose yourself to the brightest heat, the warmest color...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/c202056e0c1a20eb2178b0eeefa11c7b.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/c202056e0c1a20eb2178b0eeefa11c7b.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>/INVESTIGATE A HAUNTED CYBERPUNK HOUSE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the hidden corridors and uncover the sordid past of a house out of time and place within a futuristic cyberpunk city</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>/COLLECT CARDS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect the memory cards of three main characters, An underground cultist, an ambitious philanthropist, and a drifter. Explore their realities to help piece together your own fractured memory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>/FIGHT THE TERROR OF THE PAST.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden deep within the memories something watches you. Not every part of yourself is easy to face.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/aa2bb08103a9b5dfd05243289e83a81c.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/aa2bb08103a9b5dfd05243289e83a81c.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/aa2bb08103a9b5dfd05243289e83a81c.mp4?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>/THE YEAR IS 2489.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acid rain rots away exposed rebar in the half-developed megacity once known as Toronto. Humanity modifies itself at a frequency never seen before. One lone house remains amongst a towering landscape. A house with an inescapable past, as a group of outcasts try their best to turn it into a home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Haze, one of those outcasts. You've woken up without any memory of who, or where you are. The only clues you have are a memory card with your name on it and a vision of a color that haunts you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something about the house is wrong... The past can't be contained here... You'll have to face it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/291963bdaafaaa954beba2cab42f1777.apng?t=1768666553\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/291963bdaafaaa954beba2cab42f1777.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" class=\"bb_img\" width=500 height=151 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/e28cc3de9864c080a967952e86479365.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/e28cc3de9864c080a967952e86479365.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/e28cc3de9864c080a967952e86479365.mp4?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TIME JUMPING</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a cybernetic memory card system to navigate through time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain the perspective of others' stored memories. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain access to new parts of the house.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/102ad670e4a5eaa2b7e6289d0001a06b.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/102ad670e4a5eaa2b7e6289d0001a06b.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CYBER POSSESSION</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Allow the digital ghosts of the past to possess your body in order to descramble memories, solve puzzles, and see through their perspectives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/5621eaab1b86ef699b466b814fc27b38.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/5621eaab1b86ef699b466b814fc27b38.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/5621eaab1b86ef699b466b814fc27b38.mp4?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>INTERACTABLE SCREENS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter Haze's perspective and interact with horrifying tableaus. Pull levers, activate altars, search for hidden objects, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/af9fcd567cd87c4107838a8e93987554.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/af9fcd567cd87c4107838a8e93987554.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/af9fcd567cd87c4107838a8e93987554.mp4?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>INTRICATE PIXEL ART</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An art style that takes inspiration from the limited color palettes of the past and cyberpunk works of art like Akira, Blade Runner  and Ghost in The Shell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/9ee433c94fbc5ea4a2cbb6d636188009.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/9ee433c94fbc5ea4a2cbb6d636188009.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/9ee433c94fbc5ea4a2cbb6d636188009.mp4?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHILLING ORIGINAL SOUNDTRACK</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An experimental soundtrack steeped in the influences of classic horror and cyberpunk films.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/365daff113669b735247bf364908e4ef.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" width=718 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/365daff113669b735247bf364908e4ef.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/b3e1e05afeea20b71a0ba55cc1dce031.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/b3e1e05afeea20b71a0ba55cc1dce031.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/b3e1e05afeea20b71a0ba55cc1dce031.mp4?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Psychroma is a psychological horror side-scroller set in a haunted cyberpunk house. Collect cards and explore the memories stored on them to piece together your past. But the deeper you go, the more you expose yourself to the brightest heat, the warmest color...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/c202056e0c1a20eb2178b0eeefa11c7b.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/c202056e0c1a20eb2178b0eeefa11c7b.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>/INVESTIGATE A HAUNTED CYBERPUNK HOUSE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the hidden corridors and uncover the sordid past of a house out of time and place within a futuristic cyberpunk city</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>/COLLECT CARDS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect the memory cards of three main characters, An underground cultist, an ambitious philanthropist, and a drifter. Explore their realities to help piece together your own fractured memory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>/FIGHT THE TERROR OF THE PAST.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden deep within the memories something watches you. Not every part of yourself is easy to face.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/aa2bb08103a9b5dfd05243289e83a81c.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/aa2bb08103a9b5dfd05243289e83a81c.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/aa2bb08103a9b5dfd05243289e83a81c.mp4?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>/THE YEAR IS 2489.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acid rain rots away exposed rebar in the half-developed megacity once known as Toronto. Humanity modifies itself at a frequency never seen before. One lone house remains amongst a towering landscape. A house with an inescapable past, as a group of outcasts try their best to turn it into a home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Haze, one of those outcasts. You've woken up without any memory of who, or where you are. The only clues you have are a memory card with your name on it and a vision of a color that haunts you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something about the house is wrong... The past can't be contained here... You'll have to face it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/291963bdaafaaa954beba2cab42f1777.apng?t=1768666553\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/291963bdaafaaa954beba2cab42f1777.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" class=\"bb_img\" width=500 height=151 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/e28cc3de9864c080a967952e86479365.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/e28cc3de9864c080a967952e86479365.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/e28cc3de9864c080a967952e86479365.mp4?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TIME JUMPING</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a cybernetic memory card system to navigate through time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain the perspective of others' stored memories. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain access to new parts of the house.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/102ad670e4a5eaa2b7e6289d0001a06b.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/102ad670e4a5eaa2b7e6289d0001a06b.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CYBER POSSESSION</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Allow the digital ghosts of the past to possess your body in order to descramble memories, solve puzzles, and see through their perspectives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/5621eaab1b86ef699b466b814fc27b38.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/5621eaab1b86ef699b466b814fc27b38.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/5621eaab1b86ef699b466b814fc27b38.mp4?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>INTERACTABLE SCREENS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter Haze's perspective and interact with horrifying tableaus. Pull levers, activate altars, search for hidden objects, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/af9fcd567cd87c4107838a8e93987554.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/af9fcd567cd87c4107838a8e93987554.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/af9fcd567cd87c4107838a8e93987554.mp4?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>INTRICATE PIXEL ART</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An art style that takes inspiration from the limited color palettes of the past and cyberpunk works of art like Akira, Blade Runner  and Ghost in The Shell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/9ee433c94fbc5ea4a2cbb6d636188009.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/9ee433c94fbc5ea4a2cbb6d636188009.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/9ee433c94fbc5ea4a2cbb6d636188009.mp4?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHILLING ORIGINAL SOUNDTRACK</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An experimental soundtrack steeped in the influences of classic horror and cyberpunk films.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/365daff113669b735247bf364908e4ef.poster.avif?t=1768666553\" width=718 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879950/extras/365daff113669b735247bf364908e4ef.webm?t=1768666553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
